UK map at County/Unitary Authority level

Source: R/country-map.R
counties.Rd

Merges boundaries to County/Unitary Authority level from the unified dataset.

counties()

Value

A tibble with multipolygon geometry for each County/Unitary Authority.

Examples

counties()
